---
title: Caribbean-Style Chicken & Veggie Rice Bowl with Charred Corn Salsa & Aioli
description: The rice is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh chicken breast in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk seasoning and roast veggies with a zap of corn salsa and aioli drizzled over at the end.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with brown rice due
to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
